steps.html_instructions: Head south on N Meridian St toward E Court St

Keep right at the fork, follow signs for I-70 W/St Louis and merge onto I-70 W
Entering Illinois
Keep left at the fork to continue on I-57, follow signs for Interstate 57 S/Memphis

Keep right at the fork to continue on I-57 S, follow signs for Interstate 57 S/Memphis
Entering Missouri

Take exit 1A to merge onto I-55 S toward Memphis
Entering Arkansas
Take exit 8 to merge onto I-40 W toward Little Rock
Keep left at the fork to continue on I-30 W
Take exit 2B for Doctor Martin Luther King Junior Drive

Turn right onto Dr Martin Luther King Dr/M L King (signs for State Capitol Complex)
Continue to follow Dr Martin Luther King Dr
